            .content-block
                h1.content-block__title About Us
                .content-block__descr
                    p U.Today is a global media organisation dedicated to helping you understand the new generation tech and the future it brings to society. <br> Our mission is to serve the emerging community of enthusiasts, professionals and newcomers who explore, use and develop the tech by heeding the core journalistic values of clear thinking, accuracy and independence. <br> We seek to inform, educate, collaborate and support better practices for the benefit of all.
